description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit an enthusiastic and highly motivated Community Team secretary to work Tuesday - Friday in the Harrogate Integrated Community Mental Health Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be responsible for dealing with booking appointments, following up referrals, supporting clinicians with all aspects of admin, directing patients calls and queries. The role also covers ad reception duties as well as audio typing. Liaison with GP&#39;s and other agencies&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants should have good interpersonal skills and will need to demonstrate a commitment to working with this client group, be positive, flexible and able to promote the service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous clerical/admin experience is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Philip Donohoe - Team Manager&lt;/p&gt;
